item.dc:creator: @Coldbloodio Coldbloodio
item.description:
@Coldbloodio wrote:

Restart your computer. When it starts up don’t do anything. Go into your server files and delete the character file. If that fails, Copy all of the other characters and paste them into a new character folder. Copy your server and move it to a new folder aswell. Move the character file into it. There you go. That will fix it. Run a virus scan on your computer and see if that deletes the file.
